THINGS YOU NEED TO KNOW

The Herald Sun Pass is free. It entitles you to access 12 locked articles in 12 consecutive weeks only on the Herald Sun website and not the app. Not in conjunction with any other offer. Any unused articles at the end of that 12 weeks will be forfeited. This pass does not provide access to the +Rewards program. Only available to persons who are offered the Pass directly from the Herald Sun. A person is only entitled to one active Pass (whether to The Advertiser, The Courier-Mail, Herald Sun, The Daily Telegraph, The Australian or any other News Corp Australia publication participating in the Pass program) at any given time See www.heraldsun.com.au/subscriptionterms for full details.
